      "options": {
        "content": "## NUC Automation Schedule\n\n| Time | Job | Project | Trigger |\n|------|-----|---------|--------|\n| **20:00 Dublin** | Morning solar advisory \u2192 Pushover | Sparc | APScheduler (sparc-api) |\n| **23:30 Dublin** | myEnergi poller (Eddi/Zappi) | Sparc | APScheduler (sparc-api) |\n| **09:00 daily** | Health poller (Garmin \u2192 InfluxDB \u2192 Pushover) | Health | `docker start health-poller` |\n| **01:00 daily** | Gardening weather poller | Gardening | `docker start gardening-weather-poller` |\n| **Every 30 min** | Disk watch + auto-prune + Prometheus metrics | Infra | `docker_disk_watch.py` |\n| **Every 30s** | Container CPU/RAM metrics | Infra | `docker_stats_prom.sh` |\n\n**Metric pattern:** each project emits `<project>_poller_last_run_ts` to `/var/node_exporter/textfiles/`  \n**Auto-prune:** disk > 80% \u2192 `docker builder prune -f` | **Alert:** disk orange \u2265 75% \u00b7 red \u2265 85%",
