      "id": 60,
      "options": {
        "content": "## \u26a1 Sparc Energy Stack\n| Service | Technology | Notes |\n|---------|-----------|-------|\n| **Primary Database** | **TimescaleDB** (PostgreSQL 16) | Time-series hypertables + full SQL. Container: `sparc-db` |\n| **Cache** | Redis 7 | AOF persistence \u00b7 256 MB cap \u00b7 allkeys-lru eviction |\n| **API** | FastAPI + LightGBM | H+24 load forecast \u00b7 ControlEngine \u00b7 Solar Advisory |\n| **Automation** | n8n 2.19 | 5 active workflows (Alert Relay, Morning Brief, Drift Check). Shared with \ud83c\udf31 Gardening. |\n| **Reverse Proxy** | Caddy 2 | Auto-TLS \u00b7 HTTP/3 |\n\n## \ud83c\udf31 Gardening Stack\n| Service | Technology | Notes |\n|---------|-----------|-------|\n| **Time-series DB** | InfluxDB 2.7 | Sensor streams: soil, temp, humidity, LVPD. Container: `gardening-influxdb` |\n| **Visualisation** | Grafana OSS 11 | 25-panel dashboard \u00b7 http://localhost:3000. Container: `gardening-grafana` |\n| **Hub** | Streamlit | Live LVPD \u00b7 GDD \u00b7 harvest log \u00b7 RAG. Container: `gardening-streamlit` |\n| **Poller** | Python Ecowitt API | 5 min poll \u2192 InfluxDB. Container: `gardening-poller` |\n\n## \ud83d\udd27 Shared Infrastructure\n| Service | Technology | Notes |\n|---------|-----------|-------|\n| **Monitoring** | Prometheus v2.52 \u2192 Grafana OSS 11 | Scrapes node_exporter + textfile collector (cAdvisor workaround) |\n| **Container UI** | Portainer CE | Full Docker management \u00b7 http://localhost:9000 |\n\n> **ADR-012:** Sparc uses TimescaleDB (UPDATE/FK on `recommendations`, `households` \u2014 impossible in InfluxDB). Gardening uses InfluxDB (pure append-only sensor streams). See `docs/adr/ADR-012`.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
